Arthur J. Gallagher May Buy U.K. Broker, Sunday Telegraph Says

-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 
2011-03-27T09:19:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-27/arthur-j-gallagher-may-buy-u-k-broker-sunday-telegraph-says.html
Arthur J. Gallagher & Co., a U.S.
insurance broker, is in talks to buy Heath Lambert Ltd., a U.K.
competitor, the  Sunday Telegraph  reported today, without saying
where it got the information.  The transaction may be announced this week and could be
worth more than 100 million pounds ($160 million), the report
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rachel Graham in London 
 rgraham13@bloomberg.net  